oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of Joshua Denton Phillips of Smithville, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This photo shows Joshua Denton Phillips of Smithville, Dekalb County, Tennessee, in campaign hat and uniform. Born January 6, 1894, he died June 13, 1951 in Fulton County, Atlanta, Georgia. He was married to Susie Owens possibly from Atlanta. He worked as a photographer after the war.
